26
00:01:21,548 --> 00:01:26,847
I'll go over to the elevator that had stopped and check things out.

27
00:01:26,848 --> 00:01:27,947
No!

28
00:01:27,948 --> 00:01:31,647
That bomb has been set to lure officers there. It's a trap!

29
00:01:31,648 --> 00:01:34,947
What? A trap?

30
00:01:34,948 --> 00:01:38,547
I'll be there in 5 minutes, so wait there until I get there.

31
00:01:38,548 --> 00:01:39,747
Understand?

32
00:01:39,748 --> 00:01:41,147
Okay.

33
00:01:41,148 --> 00:01:43,348
Hey, we've got trouble!

34
00:01:44,648 --> 00:01:47,647
