35
00:01:47,648 --> 00:01:49,847
because of the explosion a while ago.

36
00:01:49,848 --> 00:01:51,747
What?

37
00:01:51,748 --> 00:01:55,147
Officer Sato, a child is in the elevator.

38
00:01:55,148 --> 00:01:56,447
Calm down.

39
00:01:56,448 --> 00:01:59,647
We've still got two hours to go before the predicted time of bombing.

40
00:01:59,648 --> 00:02:04,347
But I'd better go and check things out as soon as possible.

41
00:02:04,348 --> 00:02:05,647
Don't worry.

42
00:02:05,648 --> 00:02:08,947
I'll work something out, so you just stay there.

43
00:02:08,948 --> 00:02:10,647
But...

44
00:02:10,648 --> 00:02:12,447
Listen here, Takagi.

45
00:02:12,448 --> 00:02:15,247
Make sure Miwako stays out of dangerous situations.

46
00:02:15,248 --> 00:02:18,147
I'll rescue that girl. I promise!

47
00:02:18,148 --> 00:02:19,347
But...

48
00:02:19,348 --> 00:02:22,347
Who knows what she might do later.

49
00:02:22,348 --> 00:02:24,647
Understand? This is an order!

50
00:02:24,648 --> 00:02:28,047
You stay there until I get there.

51
00:02:28,048 --> 00:02:29,648
Understand, Officer Takagi?

52
00:02:31,148 --> 00:02:33,947
Hey, Officer Takagi. Can you hear me?

53
00:02:33,948 --> 00:02:36,647
Officer Takagi, answer me!

54
00:02:36,648 --> 00:02:38,347
Hey, Officer Takagi!

55
00:02:38,348 --> 00:02:40,347
Officer Takagi!

56
00:02:40,348 --> 00:02:42,748
Please, Officer Takagi! Don't go!

57
00:02:46,248 --> 00:02:47,948
I'm going.

58
00:02:51,548 --> 00:02:55,447
I'm going to check how things are inside.

59
00:02:55,448 --> 00:02:57,448
Officer Takagi!

60
00:03:01,348 --> 00:03:02,547
All of you!

61
00:03:02,548 --> 00:03:06,347
I'm going to go inside the tower now,

62
00:03:06,348 --> 00:03:09,147
