63
00:03:09,148 --> 00:03:10,447
What?

64
00:03:10,448 --> 00:03:12,247
Understand?

65
00:03:12,248 --> 00:03:13,847
Yes, sir.

66
00:03:13,848 --> 00:03:15,748
I'll be right back!

67
00:03:16,948 --> 00:03:19,548
I wonder if Officer Takagi is going to be okay.

68
00:03:20,948 --> 00:03:23,548
-Ai, take care of everybody, okay? -What?

69
