-Hey, Conan! -Conan!

70
00:03:27,248 --> 00:03:29,847
What? Are you going too, Conan?

71
00:03:29,848 --> 00:03:33,047
I'm just going to go check how things are.

72
00:03:33,048 --> 00:03:36,147
You guys keep watch and make sure nobody suspicious

73
00:03:36,148 --> 00:03:37,447
