103
00:05:07,148 --> 00:05:11,147
Please remain calm, and move along without rushing.

104
00:05:11,148 --> 00:05:14,047
Excuse me, police. Please let me through!

105
00:05:14,048 --> 00:05:16,147
Please don't panic.

106
00:05:16,148 --> 00:05:20,247
Police! Where's the elevator that stopped?

107
00:05:20,248 --> 00:05:22,747
It's the one at the very end.

108
00:05:22,748 --> 00:05:24,547
Thanks.

109
00:05:24,548 --> 00:05:27,647
Akemi, you'll be fine. Don't be afraid. Come on out.

110
00:05:27,648 --> 00:05:29,247
Police.

111
00:05:29,248 --> 00:05:32,547
This is the elevator that the girl is trap in?

112
00:05:32,548 --> 00:05:33,947
Yes, sir.

113
00:05:33,948 --> 00:05:35,547
-It came down from the top floor... -Akemi...

114
00:05:35,548 --> 00:05:39,747
and stopped just before reaching the observatory.

115
00:05:39,748 --> 00:05:42,747
Akemi. What are you doing, Akemi?

116
00:05:42,748 --> 00:05:45,547
Hurry and come out! Come over here!

117
00:05:45,548 --> 00:05:47,047
Akemi!

118
00:05:47,048 --> 00:05:49,547
Only one child was in the elevator

119
00:05:49,548 --> 00:05:51,847
but she's so scared that she won't listen to her mother

120
00:05:51,848 --> 00:05:54,247
telling her to come out.

121
00:05:54,248 --> 00:05:57,847
This space is too small for an adult to get through.

122
00:05:57,848 --> 00:05:59,647
Will you carry me up then?

123
00:05:59,648 --> 00:06:00,847
What?

124
00:06:00,848 --> 00:06:02,947
I can make it inside, can't I?

125
00:06:02,948 --> 00:06:04,848
Conan.

126
00:06:06,448 --> 00:06:09,847
We continue to bring you live broadcast news from Toto Tower.

127
00:06:09,848 --> 00:06:13,147
Today, at approximately 9:45 a.m.,

128
00:06:13,148 --> 00:06:15,347
there was an explosion inside Toto Tower.

129
00:06:15,348 --> 00:06:17,147
The cause of the explosion is still unknown.

130
00:06:17,148 --> 00:06:19,947
Fortunately, no casualties have been reported,

131
00:06:19,948 --> 00:06:21,347
but due to the impact of the explosion,

132
00:06:21,348 --> 00:06:24,547
one of the elevators have stopped.

133
00:06:24,548 --> 00:06:27,647
A four years old girl who happened to be on the elevator

134
00:06:27,648 --> 00:06:29,547
is trapped inside.

135
00:06:29,548 --> 00:06:33,248
Presently, while trying to find the cause of the explosion...

136
00:06:49,948 --> 00:06:51,647
Conan, are you all right?

137
00:06:51,648 --> 00:06:52,947
Yes.

138
00:06:52,948 --> 00:06:55,648
Hello, Akemi.

139
00:06:57,348 --> 00:07:01,848
I'm going to go over to you now, so hold on, okay?

140
00:07:06,448 --> 00:07:09,647
Akemi, what a cute teddy bear.

141
00:07:09,648 --> 00:07:11,648
What's its name?

142
00:07:12,648 --> 00:07:15,147
Jam.

143
00:07:15,148 --> 00:07:18,447
What a cute name! Is he a boy?

144
00:07:18,448 --> 00:07:20,347
Yes.

145
00:07:20,348 --> 00:07:24,947
I want to go over and say hello to Jam.

146
00:07:24,948 --> 00:07:26,247
Is it okay?

147
00:07:26,248 --> 00:07:27,747
Yes, it's okay.

148
00:07:27,748 --> 00:07:29,548
I'm going over there, okay?

149
00:07:30,448 --> 00:07:33,647
We just got a report that

150
00:07:33,648 --> 00:07:36,647
a police officer went into the elevator

151
00:07:36,648 --> 00:07:40,148
to rescue the girl that is trapped inside.

152
00:07:41,248 --> 00:07:44,047
What? A child went into the elevator?

153
00:07:44,048 --> 00:07:45,648
It can't be!

154
00:07:48,948 --> 00:07:54,047
And mommy bought me Jam for my birthday.

155
00:07:54,048 --> 00:07:58,247
I see. Since mommy's waiting outside, shall we go?

156
00:07:58,248 --> 00:07:59,448
Yes.

157
00:08:08,248 --> 00:08:10,648
Okay, come. Good girl.

158
00:08:12,048 --> 00:08:14,047
-Mommy! -Akemi!

159
00:08:14,048 --> 00:08:15,347
Mommy!

160
00:08:15,348 --> 00:08:16,847
-Akemi! -Mommy!

161
00:08:16,848 --> 00:08:18,548
Akemi!

162
00:08:22,548 --> 00:08:24,948
-Okay, Conan, now you. -Yes!

163
00:08:34,548 --> 00:08:35,748
Conan!

164
00:08:37,648 --> 00:08:39,048
Gosh!

165
00:08:48,948 --> 00:08:52,347
And? You went off wanting to look cool,

166
00:08:52,348 --> 00:08:55,647
and now you're trapped in the elevator with Conan.

167
00:08:55,648 --> 00:08:57,947
I'm sorry.

168
00:08:57,948 --> 00:09:03,147
By the way, are you sure there's no bomb in that elevator?

169
00:09:03,148 --> 00:09:08,547
No, there's nothing that looks like a bomb here in the elevator.

170
00:09:08,548 --> 00:09:11,648
I'm going check the top of the elevator now.

171
00:09:23,348 --> 00:09:26,747
Do you know about where you are now?

172
00:09:26,748 --> 00:09:28,447
Probably...

173
00:09:28,448 --> 00:09:30,647
All the wires seem to have been severed,

174
00:09:30,648 --> 00:09:33,247
so I think with the emergency stop

175
00:09:33,248 --> 00:09:38,247
we are in the middle of the observatory and roof of the tower building.

176
00:09:38,248 --> 00:09:39,248
Is that right?

177
00:09:39,249 --> 00:09:41,847
I guess I'll have to climb to the ceiling

178
00:09:41,848 --> 00:09:44,147
and wait for the rescue squad.

179
00:09:44,148 --> 00:09:46,247
No, don't climb up to the ceiling!

180
00:09:46,248 --> 00:09:48,847
The mercury lever will operate!

181
00:09:48,848 --> 00:09:51,547
The mercury lever?

182
00:09:51,548 --> 00:09:53,148
Mercury lever?

183
00:09:54,148 --> 00:09:57,347
A slight shake can make the mercury-drop roll,

184
00:09:57,348 --> 00:09:59,448
and if the drop touches the wire, that's it.

185
00:10:00,448 --> 00:10:04,347
Conan, what's a mercury lever?

186
00:10:04,348 --> 00:10:07,147
It's a part of the trigger device of the bomb.

187
00:10:07,148 --> 00:10:09,347
It's a bomb big enough that is capable of

188
00:10:09,348 --> 00:10:11,847
not only blowing up this elevator

189
00:10:11,848 --> 00:10:13,748
but the entire Toto Tower as well.

190
00:10:25,736 --> 00:10:28,035
A bomb?

191
00:10:28,036 --> 00:10:30,735
On the ceiling of this elevator?

192
00:10:30,736 --> 00:10:34,435
Are you sure about that, Conan?

193
00:10:34,436 --> 00:10:39,835
Yes. I saw bombs that looks just like this one on TV.

194
00:10:39,836 --> 00:10:42,935
