00:11:11,236 --> 00:11:13,535
or if the rescue squad comes down here with a rope,

206
00:11:13,536 --> 00:11:15,835
the minute they set foot on the ground

207
00:11:15,836 --> 00:11:19,536
and even if it shakes just a little bit, it's boom!

208
00:11:20,436 --> 00:11:24,135
Is it that strong?

209
00:11:24,136 --> 00:11:25,936
The mercury lever.

210
00:11:28,136 --> 00:11:29,836
Mercury lever...

211
00:11:31,536 --> 00:11:33,135
Just as I thought.

212
00:11:33,136 --> 00:11:34,635
I'm sure that the one who set this up

213
00:11:34,636 --> 00:11:37,136
is the same bomber as three years ago.

214
00:11:40,136 --> 00:11:43,936
Then, don't tell me that...

215
00:11:44,636 --> 00:11:49,535
Then, why don't we have them lower a rope from the elevator door above

216
00:11:49,536 --> 00:11:51,535
