217
00:11:51,536 --> 00:11:53,935
I don't think that will work either.

218
00:11:53,936 --> 00:11:55,135
What?

219
00:11:55,136 --> 00:11:59,735
There's wire tap near the bomb.

220
00:11:59,736 --> 00:12:02,235
So, I'm sure that as soon as the bomber

221
