224
00:12:10,836 --> 00:12:14,735
Which means we're trapped either way.

225
00:12:14,736 --> 00:12:17,336
No, we still have one way out.

226
00:12:20,536 --> 00:12:23,635
I have to disassemble this bomb.

227
00:12:23,636 --> 00:12:27,036
I need them to lower the bomb disposal tool from above though.

228
00:12:30,536 --> 00:12:31,935
I repeat.

229
00:12:31,936 --> 00:12:34,035
All citizens within the vicinity of Toto Tower,

230
00:12:34,036 --> 00:12:38,435
