00:13:49,836 --> 00:13:51,235
Roger!

255
00:13:51,236 --> 00:13:54,235
We've completed giving the equipment.

256
00:13:54,236 --> 00:13:55,535
Okay.

257
00:13:55,536 --> 00:13:59,435
Okay, Officer Takagi, let's start.

258
00:13:59,436 --> 00:14:00,735
Yes, sir.

